ill have to watch out for not only the law but competitors as well.Rogues can be found among all the races and in almost any setting. Their roles vary from spies and troubleshooters to burglars, bandits, and thugs. \r\n	   	 \r\n	   	\r\n	   	 Roles: \r\n	   	 Thief, burglar, smuggler, scout, spy, troubleshooter. \r\n	   	 \r\n	   	\r\n	   	 Ranks: \r\n	   	 Rogue (Apprentice), Footpad, Cutpurse, Robber, Burglar, Filcher, Sharper, Magsman, Thief, Master ThiefBravo (Apprentice), Rutterkin, Waghalter, Murderer, Thug, Killer, Cutthroat, Executioner, Assassin, Expert Assassin, Senior Assassin, Chief Assassin, Prime Assassin, Grandmaster Assassin, Grandfather Assassin \r\n	   	 \r\n	     \r\n		    \r\n		    \r\n		     \r\n		     Rogue Configuration: \r\n		   	 Assassin \r\n		   	  \r\n		   	\r\n		   	 Primary Skills: \r\n		   	 Acrob, Athle, Percp, Steal, Thiev, WpNat, WpFnc, WpCrs, WpSmT, ArmLt, DaSns, FSMul, FSPre, VitAt \r\n		   	 \r\n		   	\r\n		   	 Secondary Skills: \r\n		   	 Perfm, Psych, SCtrl, WpGen, CmbIn, FSMob, FSTri, ArcIl \r\n		   	 \r\n		     \r\n		    \r\n		    \r\n		     \r\n		     Rogue Configuration: \r\n		   	 Rogue \r\n		   	  \r\n		   	\r\n		   	 Primary Skills: \r\n		   	 Acrob, Athle, Percp, SCtrl, Steal, Thiev, WpGen, WpFnc, WpSmT, DaSns, FSMul, FSMob, VitAt \r\n		   	 \r\n		   	\r\n		   	 Secondary Skills: \r\n		   	 Know, Psych, ArmLt, CmbIn, FSPow, FSTri, ArcDi, ArcIl, ArcTr, PsMag \r\n		   	 \r\n		     \r\n		    \r\n		    \r\n		     \r\n		     Rogue Configuration: \r\n		   	 Smuggler \r\n		   	  \r\n		   	\r\n		   	 Primary Skills: \r\n		   	 Craft, Know, Percp, Steal, Thiev, WpLtB, WpSmT, DaSns, FSMul, PsMag \r\n		   	 \r\n		   	\r\n		   	 Secondary Skills: \r\n		   	 Lingu, Psych, WpGen, ArmLt, FSMob, FSTri, ArcDi, ArcIl, ArcTr \r\n		   	 \r\n		     \r\n		    \r\n		    \r\n		     \r\n		     Rogue Configuration: \r\n		   	 Spy \r\n		   	  \r\n		   	\r\n		   	 Primary Skills: \r\n		   	 Acrob, Athle, Lingu, Percp, SCtrl, Steal, Thiev, WpFnc, WpSmT, DaSns, FSMul, VitAt \r\n		   	 \r\n		   	\r\n		   	 Secondary Skills: \r\n		   	 Psych, WpGen, WpLtB, ArmLt, FSMob, FSTri, ArcIl, PsMag \r\n		   	 \r\n		     \r\n		    \r\n		    \r\n		     \r\n		     Rogue Configuration: \r\n		   	 Thug \r\n		   	  \r\n		   	\r\n		   	 Primary Skills: \r\n		   	 Athle, WpNat, WpBrl, WpGen, WpFnc, WpCrs, WpSmT, ArmLt, CmbIn, FSMul, FSTri, VitAt \r\n		   	 \r\n		   	\r\n		   	 Secondary Skills: \r\n		   	 Psych, Steal, Thiev, FSMob, FSPow \r\n		   	 \r\n		     \r\n	    \r\n	    \r\n	     \r\n	     Class: \r\n	   	 Templar (Tmp) \r\n	   	  \r\n	   	\r\n	   	 HP/Level: \r\n	   	 10 \r\n	   	 \r\n	   	\r\n	   	 SP/Level: \r\n	   	 6 \r\n	   	 \r\n	   	\r\n	   	 PP/Level: \r\n	   	 4 \r\n	   	 \r\n	   	\r\n	   	 Infl/Level: \r\n	   	 5 \r\n	   	 \r\n	   	\r\n	   	 Skill Pts/Level: \r\n	   	 18 \r\n	   	 \r\n	   	\r\n	   	 Key Ability Scores: \r\n	   	 Cha, Str, Wis \r\n	   	 \r\n	   	\r\n	   	 Favored Alignment: \r\n	   	 Any (same as deity) \r\n	   	 \r\n	   	\r\n	   	 Spell Knowledge: \r\n	   	 A templar\'s church will teach him most of the spells that he has sufficient divine skills to cast.More unusual spells can be learned from a teacher, divine writings, personal prayers, etc. \r\n	   	 \r\n	   	\r\n	   	 Role-Playing Notes: \r\n	   	 Templars are devoted to a deity or philosophy, and they follow a strict code of conduct appropriate to this devotion and the deity\'s alignment. For example, a lawful good templar should respect life, protect the weak, help those in need, respect legitimate authority, never lie or cheat, and punish the wicked.Most templars are trained within the church of their deity or philosophy. Some, however, find their calling outside any official religion and simply follow their own conscience.Most templars are humans or half-elves, although a rare few are dwarves or elves.A templar who knowingly and willingly commits an act clearly opposite to his alignment loses all divine abilities forever. Those who violate their code of conduct lose all divine abilities until they have atoned. \r\n	   	 \r\n	   	\r\n	   	 Roles: \r\n	   	 Knight, templar, champion, protector, bodyguard, justiciar. \r\n	   	 \r\n	   	\r\n	   	 Ranks: \r\n	   	 Gallant, Keeper, Protector, Defender, Warder, Guardian, Chevalier, Justicer, Paladin \r\n	   	 \r\n	     \r\n		    \r\n		    \r\n		     \r\n		     Templar Configuration: \r\n		   	 Templar of Freedom \r\n		   	  \r\n		   	\r\n		   	 Primary Skills: \r\n		   	 Heal, Ride, WpGen, WpHvB, WpShd, WpSpr, ArmHv, CmbIn, FSPow, FSPre, DvMnt, DvPro, DvSmi \r\n		   	 \r\n		   	\r\n		   	 Secondary Skills: \r\n		   	 Psych, Warfr, DivBl, DivIn, DivLi, DivPr, DivRe, DivSu, CAGoo, SplCr \r\n		   	 \r\n		     \r\n		    \r\n		    \r\n		     \r\n		     Templar Configuration: \r\n		   	 Templar of Honor \r\n		   	  \r\n		   	\r\n		   	 Primary Skills: \r\n		   	 Heal, Ride, WpGen, WpHvB, WpShd, WpSpr, ArmHv, CmbIn, FSPow, FSPre, DvMnt, DvPro, DvSmi \r\n		   	 \r\n		   	\r\n		   	 Secondary Skills: \r\n		   	 Psych, Warfr, DivBl, DivIn, DivLi, DivPr, DivRe, DivSu, CAGoo, SplCr \r\n		   	 \r\n		     \r\n		    \r\n		    \r\n		     \r\n		     Templar Configuration: \r\n		   	 Templar of Slaughter \r\n		   	  \r\n		   	\r\n		   	 Primary Skills: \r\n		   	 Ride, WpGen, WpHvB, WpShd, WpSpr, ArmHv, CmbIn, FSPow, FSPre, DvMnt, DvPro, DvSmi \r\n		   	 \r\n		   	\r\n		   	 Secondary Skills: \r\n		   	 Heal, Psych, VitAt, Warfr, DivBl, DivDe, DivIn, DivPr, DivRe, DivSu, CAEvi, SplCr \r\n		   	 \r\n		     \r\n		    \r\n		    \r\n		     \r\n		     Templar Configuration: \r\n		   	 Templar of Tyranny \r\n		   	  \r\n		   	\r\n		   	 Primary Skills: \r\n		   	 Ride, WpGen, WpHvB, WpShd, WpSpr, ArmHv, CmbIn, FSPow, FSPre, DvMnt, DvPro, DvSmi \r\n		   	 \r\n		   	\r\n		   	 Secondary Skills: \r\n		   	 Heal, Psych, VitAt, Warfr, DivBl, DivDe, DivIn, DivPr, DivRe, DivSu, CAEvi, SplCr \r\n		   	 \r\n		     \r\n	    \r\n	    \r\n	     \r\n	     Class: \r\n	   	 Wizard (Wiz) \r