 \r\n				   	Adept Affinity Benefits \r\n				     \r\n				     Level \r\n				   	 Benefits \r\n				   	  \r\n1  Supernatural affinity (Arcane; Wis; PP reduction (lvl+WisMod)/5); Prereq: EC=1 AND Skl(WpNat)>=1 					\r\n				    \r\n				   	Ki - Study of Earth Benefits \r\n				     \r\n				     Level \r\n				   	 Benefits \r\n				   	  \r\n1  +(lvl+2)/3 skill modifier to damage; Prereq: Weapon==WpNat +(lvl+1)/3 modifier on checks to maintain balance and resist forced movement   4  Improved bull rush (no AoO)   6  Improved overrun (target cannot choose to avoid; success grants a free leg attack against target)   8  Greater bull rush (target\'s movement triggers AoO)   10  Greater overrun (target\'s falling prone triggers AoO)   			     \r\n Ki - Study of Fire (KiSFi)  Ki - Study of Fire is a martial arts skill that emulates aspects of fire in your natural weapon attacks as well as with certain selected weapons.Inspired by the 3.5E Monk class.  Prerequisites: Skl(KiOff)>=1 AND Skl(WpExo)>=1 					\r\n				    \r\n				   	Ki - Study of Fire Benefits \r\n				     \r\n				     Level \r\n				   	 Benefits \r\n				   	  \r\n1  +(lvl+1)/3 skill modifier to attacks; Prereq: Weapon==WpMnk +lvl/3 skill modifier to damage; Prereq: Weapon==WpMnk +(lvl+2)/3 skill parry modifier (DeC); Prereq: Weapon==WpMnk   4  Slowing Strike (special action)   8  Deafening Strike (special action)   10  Silencing Strike (special action)   12  Blinding Strike (special action)   15  Paralyzing Strike (special action)   18  Steel Cloth (special action)   			     \r\n					\r\n				    \r\n				   	Ki - Study of Fire Actions \r\n				     \r\n				     Action \r\n				   	 Action Check \r\n				   	  \r\n Blinding Strike*  (Natural/monk weapon attack vs. DeC) + (d20 + Ki - Study of Fire / 2 + Wis mod + MAM + AB vs. Fort)   Deafening Strike*  (Natural/monk weapon attack vs. DeC) + (d20 + Ki - Study of Fire / 2 + Wis mod + MAM + AB vs. Fort)   Paralyzing Strike*  (Natural/monk weapon attack vs. DeC) + (d20 + Ki - 