ing heard while moving up to half your normal speed (x2 MP for moving).   Results:  S - You escape detection.F - Someone hears you.   Modifiers:  Move up to your full speed: -5Running, charging: -20Noisy surface: -2Very noisy surface: -5Swimming underwater: +5Flying: +10     Action:  Ride - [Untrained, Move]    Action Check:  d20 + Riding skill + Dex mod + PAM vs. DC   Action Time:  As per move   Range:  Personal   Duration:  1 check per round   Target(s)/Area:  You   Description:  You try to control your mount\'s movement.   Results:  S - You successfully direct your mount.F - The mount does not do what you want and moves erratically. Try again next round.   Difficulties:  Ride at base speed: 0Guide with knees: 5 (frees up both hands)Leap (as per mount\'s Athletics): 15Spur mount: 15 (increase base speed by 2 sq for 1 r)Untrained mount in combat: +15 (+5 AP cost for success; 10 AP cost for failure)Trained mount in combat: +0 (trained mounts automatically move as directed)   Modifiers:  Unsuitable mount (e.g. bipedal): -5No saddle: -5 circMilitary saddle: +2 circAnimal Empathy synergy: +1 syn per 5 lvls     Action:  Run - [Untrained, Move]    Action Time:  Full-round action   Implements:  C   Cost:  2 SP   Description:  You can run a number of squares equal to 3 times your adjusted speed.Reduce your normal maneuverability by one step.You cannot run through obstructed squares, and while running, you can only use passive DeC.     Action:  Speed of Thought - [Su]    Action Time:  0 AP   Implements:  C   Cost:  3 PP   Range:  Personal   Duration:  1 r   Target(s)/Area:  You   Description:  Speed of Thought: You can spend 3 PP to gain a +1 enhancement bonus to speed for 1 round.     Action:  Sprint - [Untrained, Move]    Action Time:  Full-round action   Implements:  C   Cost:  4 SP   Description:  You can sprint a number of squares equal to 4 times your adjusted speed.Reduce your normal maneuverability by two steps.You cannot sprint through obstructed squares, and while