ape and direction of the darkness can be controlled each round. For example, you can turn it into a cone (like a bullseye lantern) or shape the darkness itself into a vaguely humanoid figure.Deep darkness option: The radius is 12 squares (instead of 4).Blacklight option: You are yourself not affected by the spell\'s area of darkness.     Spell:  Deflective Shield - [Su, MR, AoO]    Skill(s):  Arcane - AbjurationDivine - ProtectionPsi - Psychokinesis (target you only)   Action Time:  9 AP (+0)6 AP (+6)Reaction (+10)   Implements:  V (+0), Silent (+2)S (+0), Still (+2)   Cost:  1 PP for +1 bonus+4 PP per additional +1+2 PP for projectile protection+4 PP for shadow shield   Range:  Personal or Tch (+0)Close (+3)   Duration:  Encounter (D; +0)1 h (D; +4)1 day (D; +8)1 month (D; +12)1 year (D; +14)Permanent (D; +16)   Target/Area:  You (+0)1 creature (+2)2 creatures (+4)3-4 creatures (+6)5-8 creatures (+8)9-16 creatures (+10)   Description:  You protect the target with a shimmering shield that provides a deflection bonus to DeC.   Options:  Projectile protection option: The target gains an additional +4 deflection bonus against projectiles, thrown weapons, and other ranged weapon attacks.Shadow shield option (req Arcane - Illumination; [Dark]): The shield becomes shadowy and grants the target concealment. The target also gains a +2 circumstance bonus to defenses against [Light] and [Radiant] effects.     Spell:  Detect Alignment - [Su, AoO]    Skill(s):  Divine - InsightPsi - Clairsentience   Action Time:  9 AP (+0)6 AP (+6)   Implements:  V (+0), Silent (+2)S (+0), Still (+2)   Cost:  1 PP for one aspect+1 PP for fast detection+4 PP for all aspects   Range:  0 (+0)   Duration:  Concentration (+0)Encounter (D; +2)1 h (D; +4)1 day (D; +6)1 month (D; +8)1 year (D; +10)Permanent (D; +12)   Target/Area:  Conical emanation; 12 sq (+0), 24 sq (+2), 50 sq (+4), 100 sq (+6)   Description:  You detect the presence of one particular alignment aspect (good, evil, law, or chaos), ch