m ground: 15\\nHard ground (or streambed): 20\\nPer 3 creatures being tracked: -1\\nSize of creature being tracked: -8 to +8\\nPer 24 h since trail was made: +1\\nPer hour of rain: +1\\nFresh snow cover: +10\\nPoor visibility or light: +3 to +6\\nIf the tracked creatures try to cover their tracks (requires 1/2 move), add their Survival skill to the DC.\\nWhen using scent to track, the base DC is 10, and you can ignore penalties due to surface and visibility conditions.','Move at normal speed: -5 (penalty reduced to 0 at skill level 8)\\nMove at twice normal speed: -20 (penalty reduced to -10 at skill level 8)\\nPerception synergy: +1 syn per 5 lvls',NULL,1),(100,'Predict Weather',1,'[Untrained, Secret]','d20! + Survival skill + Wis mod vs. DC','1 min',NULL,'C',NULL,'Spcl','1+ days','Local','You try to predict the weather.','S - You predict next day\'s weather (plus one additional day per 5 levels of success).\\nF - You fail to predict the weather but can try again the next day.','Predict the weather: 15',NULL,NULL,NULL),(101,'Survive Weather',1,'[Untrained]','d20! + Survival skill + Wis mod vs. DC','1 day (50% time)',NULL,'C',NULL,'Spcl','1 day',NULL,'You protect yourself (and others) against severe weather effects.','S - You can move half your overland speed and simultaneously give yourself a +2 bonus on defenses against severe temperatures and weather. If you remain stationary, you gain a +4 bonus. For every level of success, one additional person can be protected.\\nF - You do not receive any bonus but can try again the next day.','Survive weather: 15',NULL,NULL,NULL),(102,'Use Rope',1,'[Untrained, Secret]','d20! + Survival skill + Dex mod + MAM vs. DC','Var',NULL,'C, rope',NULL,'Tch',NULL,'Rope','You try to tie a special knot, splice ropes, or tie up a prisoner.','S - You successfully tie a knot that performs as desired.\\nF - You fail to tie the desired knot. You can try again.\\nOF - You believe the knot has been successfully tied.','Tie a firm knot: 10 (1 r)\