ppens during the nights of a full moon and every time you first take damage during a combat encounter. You are allowed a Control Transformation check to avoid changing shape. The shapechange is a grade II change.\\nSkill level 1: You are now able to attempt voluntary changes to your animal form and back to humanoid form.\\nSkill level 2: You are now able to attempt voluntary changes to and from a hybrid form. This too is a grade II shapechange. You still need to make checks to remember your actions and to avoid alignment change.\\nSkill level 5: You no longer need to make checks to remember your actions or avoid alignment change.\\nSkill level 8: The change of shape now takes 6 AP instead of a full round.','S - You manage to resist or trigger the transformation.\\nF - You fail to resist or trigger the change. If it is an involuntary change or a change to humanoid form, it takes 1 day before you can retry.','Resist involuntary change: 25\\nVoluntary change to humanoid form (full moon): 25\\nVoluntary change to humanoid form (not full moon): 20\\nVoluntary change to hybrid form: 15\\nVoluntary change to animal form (full moon): 15\\nVoluntary change to animal form (not full moon): 20',NULL,NULL,NULL),(191,'Gaze Attack',12,'[Su]','d20! + Body & Mind skill + PAM vs. Fort','6 AP',NULL,'C, vision',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'+1 attack bonus per AP',NULL),(192,'Elan Psi Defense',12,'[Su]',NULL,'3 AP',NULL,'C','2 PP','Personal','1 r','You','Gain +4 racial bonus to Fort, Ref, or Will for 1 round.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(193,'Elan Psi Conversion',12,'[Su]',NULL,'Reaction','You are about to take HP and/or SP damage.',NULL,'Spcl','Personal','Instantaneous','You','Once per round, when taking HP or SP damage, you can choose to convert all or part of it to PP damage.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(197,'Psi Cannibalization',11,'[Su]',NULL,'4 AP',NULL,'C','Spcl','Personal','Instantaneous','You','You can recover PP at the expense of your own health. You recover 2 PP per