amage.\\nF - The target avoids the overrun attack.\\nCF - The vehicle itself takes damage as shown for S.',NULL,'Below minimum crew: -10 or worse\\nEnvironmental conditions: varies\\nTarget has more than two legs: -4\\nEach additional target after the first: -4 (cumulative)',NULL,NULL),(304,'Vehicle Evasion',8,'[Untrained]','d20! + Profession (Driver, Sailor, or Pilot) + Wis mod + MAM vs. DC','Full round',NULL,'Var',NULL,'Personal','1 check per round','You and vehicle','You try to move your vehicle in an evasive or defensive manner.','S - You can move, turn, and accelerate or decelerate the vehicle according to its speed and maneuverability. The vehicle gains a +2 dodge bonus to DeC for 1 round.\\nES - Same as S, but with a +4 dodge bonus to DeC for both the vehicle and all passengers.\\nCS - Same as S, but with a +6 dodge bonus to DeC for both the vehicle and all passengers.\\nF - Vehicle continues moving straight at current speed.\\nCF - You lose control of the vehicle and cause damage to it (DM\'s discretion).',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(305,'Parry Melee Attack',9,'[Untrained, Boost]','Melee attack roll vs. incoming attack roll','Reaction','A melee attack is made against your DeC. You are made aware of the attack\'s level of success before choosing to react or not.','Melee weapon',NULL,'Personal','Instantaneous','One melee attack','You can attempt to parry a melee attack that would otherwise strike you.','S - You parry the attack and take no damage from it.\\nCS - You can deflect the attack against another target. As part of the reaction, make an attack roll as if using the appropriate weapon but with a -4 penalty.\\nF - You fail to parry the attack and take normal damage.',NULL,'Ki - Defense synergy: +1 per 5 lvls','+1 attack bonus per AP',NULL),(306,'Aid Ally',3,'[Untrained]','Melee attack roll vs. DeC - 10','As per attack',NULL,'As per attack','As per attack','Weapon\'s reach','Up to 1 r','1 target and 1 ally','You use a melee attack action to distract an opponent 