 [Su]: You can communicate telepathically with your psicrystal to a range of 1 km (no AP cost).\\nWhen the psicrystal is within 1 sq, you gain a +2 skill level bonus on Perception.\\nWhen the psicrystal is within 1 km, you gain a bonus based on the crystal\'s personality.\\nAny power you manifest on yourself can automatically affect your psicrystal as well (1 sq range; no extra cost; effect ends if the psicrystal moves more than 1 sq from master).\\nWhen the psicrystal is within 1 sq, it can use your Fort, Ref, and Will defenses (if they are better than its own).\\nInspired by the 3.5E Psion class.'),(190,'Psionic Mobility','PsMob',8,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Psionic Mobility is an ability that lets you use mental strength to enhance your speed and mobility.\\nInspired by the 3.5E psionic feats.'),(191,'Psionic Offense','PsOff',8,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Psionic Offense is an ability that lets you use mental strength to enhance your weapon attacks.\\nInspired by the 3.5E psionic feats.'),(192,'Pyrokinetics','Pyrok',10,NULL,'Skl(ArcPy)>=5 OR Skl(PsiPk)>=5','MAX(Skl(ArcPy)-5,Skl(PsiPk)-5)','Pyrokinetics is a supernatural ability that lets you create and control fire in different forms. Most individuals who learn this skill have volatile, chaotic, and violent personalities, and they are not always welcome in civilized societies.\\nInspired by the 3.5E Pyrokineticist prestige class.'),(193,'Shadowdancing','ShaDa',10,NULL,'Skl(Steal)>=7 AND Skl(Acrob)>=7 AND Skl(CmbIn)>=7','MIN(Skl(Steal)-7,MIN(Skl(Acrob)-7,Skl(CmbIn)-7))','Shadowdancing is a skill that gradually strengthens your connection to the Plane of Shadow and gives you supernatural abilities related to that plane.\\nInspired by the 3.5E Shadowdancer prestige class.'),(194,'Soulknife','SouKn',10,NULL,'Skl(WpLtB)>=3 AND Skl(PsiPm)>=3','MIN(Skl(WpLtB)-3,Skl(PsiPm)-3)','Soulknife is a supernatural ability that lets you use psionic energy to manifest a semi-real blade of force.\\nInspired by the 3.5E Soulknife class.'),(195,'Spellcraft','SplCr',8,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Spellcraft is a skill that develops your sensitivity to and proficiency with supernatural energies.'),(196,'Spellfire','SplFi',10,NULL,'Skl(ArcAb)>=13 AND Skl(ArcKi)>=13 AND Skl(ArcPy)>=13 AND Skl(ArcTr)>=13','MIN(Skl(ArcAb)-13,MIN(Skl(ArcKi)-13,MIN(Skl(ArcPy)-13,Skl(ArcTr)-13)))','Spellfire is the rare and powerful ability to summon and shape raw arcane energy. Powerful sorcerers and wizards sometimes learn this skill, but the most skilled spellfire wielders are the precious few born with the ability. Spellfire is a more instinctive use of magic than ordinary spellcasting. While most magic is mentally taxing, a spellfire wielder instead uses his physical stamina.\\nInspired by the 3.5E Spellfire feat.'),(197,'Wild Shape','WldSh',8,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Wild Shape is a supernatural skill that lets you assume the shapes of various animals and eventually plants and elementals.\\nInspired by the 3.5E Druid class.'),(198,'Ghost Manifestation','Ghost',9,NULL,'Race==Ghost','Race==Ghost ? TL : 0','Ghost Manifestation is a skill that ghosts (and maybe other incorporeal undead creatures) use to improve their influence over the physical world.'),(199,'Lycanthropic Control','Lycan',9,NULL,'CrSubt==Lycanthrope','CrSubt==Lycanthrope ? TL : 0','Lycanthropic Control is a skill that lycanthropic creatures use to improve and control their supernatural abilities. Natural (inherited) lycanthropes usually learn this skill as part of their upbringing, while those with acquired lycanthropy gain access to it when they contract the disease.'),(200,'Vampire Powers','VampP',9,NULL,'Race==Vampire','Race==Vampire ? TL : 0','Vampire Powers is a skill that vampires learn to gradually improve their supernatural abilities and gain new ones.'),(201,'Fighting Style - Power Attack','FSPow',3,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Fighting Style - Power Attack is a skill that focuses on strong melee attacks, favoring heavy and usually two-handed weapons.'),(202,'Fighting Style - Precision','FSPre',3,NUL