stores all ability damage and ability drain.\\nLife force option: Restores any levels and/or AP drained recently (up to 1 day per skill level).',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(62,'Cure Fatigue','[Su, MR, AoO, Radiant]','Divine - Life\\nPsi - Psychometabolism (target you only)',NULL,'7+TPC AP','V (+0), Silent (+2)\\nS (+0), Still (+2)','1 PP for 10 SP\\n+2 PP per additional 5 SP','Tch (+0)\\nClose (+3; LoS)','Instantaneous (+0)','1 creature (+0)\\n2 creatures (+2)\\n3-4 creatures (+4)\\n5-8 creatures (+6)\\n9-16 creatures (+8)','You channel radiant energy into the target creature(s), using it to cure their fatigue. When this spell is cast on multiple targets, each target is cured of the same amount (up to its maximum).',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(63,'Curse','[Su, MR, AoO]','Divine - Retribution','(Rch: d20! + Dex mod + Weapons - Natural skill + MAM + others mods vs. DeC and then)\\nd20! + Wis mod + Body & Mind skill + MAM + other mods vs. Will','7+TPC AP','V (+0), Silent (+2)\\nS (+0), Still (+2)\\nF (divine focus)','0 PP\\n+1 PP per -1 action penalty (max -5)\\n+1 PP per -1 defense penalty (max -5)\\n+1 PP per -1 ability score decrease (max -6 and to minimum 1)\\n+9 PP per reroll','Rch (+0)\\nClose (+3; LoS)\\nMedium (+6; LoS)','Encounter (D; +0)\\nOngoing (+4; 1 PP/h)\\nPermanent (D; +8; 100 XP cost per PL)','1 creature (+0)\\n2 creatures (+2)\\n3-4 creatures (+4)\\n5-8 creatures (+6)\\n9-16 creatures (+8)','You give the targets the specified divine penalty on action checks (including all attacks), defenses and/or ability scores. The caster chooses which ability score(s) to affect.\\nThe reroll option means that the next d20 check made by the target requires rolling twice and using the worse result.','Mark option: The curse includes a highly visible mark of some sort. The mark has no special effects other than being difficult to hide.\\nSilence option: The targets become unable to speak (or whistle, whisper, shout, cast verbal spells, utter command words, etc).\\nTriggered 