ent (D; +8; 100 XP cost per PL)','You (+0)\\n1 creature (+2)\\n2 creatures (+4)\\n3-4 creatures (+6)\\n5-8 creatures (+8)\\n9-16 creatures (+10)','You protect the target with a shimmering shield that provides a deflection bonus to DeC. Maximum total deflection bonus is +6 (or +10 against ranged if that extra bonus is paid for).','Projectile protection option: The target gains an additional +4 deflection bonus against projectiles, thrown weapons, and other ranged weapon attacks.\\nShadow shield option (req Arcane - Illumination; [Dark]): The shield becomes shadowy and grants the target concealment. The target also gains a +2 circumstance bonus to defenses against [Light] and [Radiant] effects.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(66,'Detect Alignment','[Su, AoO]','Divine - Insight\\nPsi - Clairsentience',NULL,'7+TPC AP','V (+0), Silent (+2)\\nS (+0), Still (+2)','1 PP for one aspect\\n+1 PP for fast detection\\n+4 PP for all aspects','0 (+0)','Concentration (+0)\\nOngoing (+4; 1 PP/h)\\nPermanent (D; +8; 100 XP cost per PL)','Conical emanation; 12 sq (+0), 24 sq (+2), 50 sq (+4), 100 sq (+6)','You detect the presence of one particular alignment aspect (good, evil, law, or chaos), chosen at the time of casting. Typically, only strongly aligned creatures (e.g. most outsiders, clerics, templars) and objects (relics and some religious items) will be detectable.\\nFast detection: A single scan gives all the information (see below).\\nAll aspects: You detect all four alignment aspects at the same time.','Fast detection option: A single scan gives all the information (see below).\\nAll aspects option: You detect all four alignment aspects at the same time.','1st round - You detect the presence or absence of the chosen alignment aspect.\\n2nd round - You detect the number of auras of the chosen aspect.\\n3rd round - You detect the location and approximate strength of each aura.',NULL,NULL,NULL),(67,'Detect Life','[Su, AoO]','Arcane - Divination and Necromancy\\nDivine - Insight and (Life 