 anchor at your current location. This anchor gives you a +10 bonus to all future attempts to locate, scry on, or teleport to this location.\\nDistance option: You sense distance as well as direction to the target.\\nFind the path option: For as long as the duration lasts, you instinctively know the most direct physical route to the target.\\nExact location option: You not only sense direction and distance to the target but also reveal the exact name of its location.\\nGuidance option: Same as find the path option, but it also reveals traps and obstacles on the way (and any passwords required to bypass them, if any).','S - You find the target\'s location.\\nF - You fail to find the target.','You have never seen the target: -4',NULL,NULL),(74,'Disintegrate','[Su, MR, AoO]','Arcane - Transmutation\\nPsi - Psychoportation\\nCleric Affinity - Destruction Domain','d20! + Dex mod + weapon skill + MAM + other mods vs. DeC\\nand then d20! + Con mod + Body & Mind skill + MAM + other mods vs. Fort','7+TPC AP','V (+0), Silent (+2)\\nS (+0), Still (+2)','1 PP for 3d6 HP\\n+1 PP per additional d6 HP','Rch (+0)\\nClose (+3; LoE)\\nMedium (+6; LoE)','Instantaneous (+0)','Ray or 1 touched target (+0)','You shoot a ray at or touch a target creature or object of solid matter, trying to disintegrate it (dealing unspecified damage type). Any creature killed by this or any object reduced to 0 HP is completely turned to fine dust. The equipment of a struck creature is not affected.\\nAgainst large objects, the ray disintegrates a maximum of 25 cubic meters (or more specifically 2x2x2 sq).\\nAny force effect struck by this spell is automatically destroyed.',NULL,'If the touch or ray hits an object, the spell deals the specified damage. If it hits a creature, a further attack against Fort has the following effect:\\nS - The spell deals the indicated damage.\\nCS - The spell deals double damage.\\nF - The spell deals only one-quarter damage.',NULL,'+1 attack bonus per AP',NULL),(75,'Dispel 