arget.',NULL,'+1 attack bonus per AP',NULL),(197,'Touch of Lightning','[Su, MR, AoO, Electricity]','Arcane - Aeromancy\\nPsi - Psychokinesis (+2 PP cost)','d20! + Dex mod + Natural Weapon skill + MAM + other mods vs. DeC','7+TPC AP','V (+0), Silent (+2)\\nS (+0), Still (+2)','1 PP for 3d6 HP/SP\\n+1 PP per additional 1d6','Rch (+0)','Instantaneous (+0)','1 target (+0)','You attack the target with a touch of electricity. You can divide the d6s of damage any way you want between HP and SP.',NULL,'S - The target takes the indicated amount of damage.\\nCS - The target takes double damage.\\nF - You hit with a glancing touch that deals half damage\\nEF - You miss the target.',NULL,'+1 attack bonus per AP',NULL),(198,'Touch of Radiance','[Su, MR, AoO, Radiant]','Arcane - Illumination\\nDivine - Life and Retribution','d20! + Dex mod + Natural Weapon skill + MAM + other mods vs. DeC','7+TPC AP','V (+0), Silent (+2)\\nS (+0), Still (+2)','1 PP for 3d6 HP\\n+1 PP per additional 1d6 HP','Rch (+0)','Instantaneous (+0)','1 target (+0)','You attack the target with a touch of intense radiance.',NULL,'S - The target takes the indicated amount of damage.\\nCS - The target takes double damage.\\nF - You hit with a glancing touch that deals half damage\\nEF - You miss the target.',NULL,'+1 attack bonus per AP',NULL),(199,'Touch of Sound','[Su, MR, AoO, Sonic]','Arcane - Aeromancy\\nPsi - Psychokinesis (+2 PP cost)\\nBardic Music','d20! + Dex mod + Natural Weapon skill + MAM + other mods vs. DeC','7+TPC AP','V (+0), Silent (+2)\\nS (+0), Still (+2)','1 PP for 3d6 HP/SP\\n+1 PP per additional 1d6','Rch (+0)','Instantaneous (+0)','1 target (+0)','You attack the target with a touch of sonic concussion. You can divide the d6s of damage any way you want between HP and SP.','Deafening option: A successful attack also deafens the target for the rest of the encounter.\\nStunning option: A successful attack also stuns the target for 1 round.','S - The target takes the indicated amount of damage.\\nCS - The target takes double damage.\\nF - You hit with a glancing touch that deals half damage\\nEF - You miss the target.',NULL,'+1 attack bonus per AP',NULL),(200,'Silver Storm','[Su, MR, AoO, Earth]','Arcane - Lithomancy\\nDivine - Elements',NULL,'7+TPC AP','V (+0), Silent (+2)\\nS (+0), Still (+2)','3 PP','Close (+0; LoE)\\nMedium (+3; LoE)','1 r (+0)\\nEncounter (D; +4)\\nOngoing (+8; 1 PP/h)','Circular spread; 4 sq rad (+0), 6 sq rad (+4)','You conjure a swirling cloud of silver particles in the chosen area. The particles cling to (and reveal) both invisible and incorporeal creatures; they also glow slightly and negate penalties due to non-magical darkness or dim light. These effects last only while a creature remains within the cloud.\\nWhile within the area, a creature suffers 1d6 SP per round (due to suffocation) and is automatically dazzled. Creatures sensitive to silver also suffer 1d10 HP of damage per round.','Needles option: The silver particles become needles that deal an additional 5d6 HP of continuous piercing damage per round. Against creatures sensitive to silver the damage increases to 5d10 HP.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(201,'Enchant Armor','[Su, AoO]','Arcane - Abjuration and Transmutation\\nDivine - Protection\\nPsi - Metacreativity',NULL,'7+TPC AP','V (+0), Silent (+2)\\nS (+0), Still (+2)','1 PP per total PL','Tch (+0)','Encounter (D; +0)\\nOngoing (+4; 1 PP/h)\\nPermanent (D; +8; 100 XP cost per PL)','1 armor (+0)','Enchants a suit of armor (or even clothing) with an enhancement bonus to DR and/or other special effects (those item modifications that have armor as preferred item type).\\nThe casting costs 1 PP per resulting PL of the armor (see the item modification list for possible effects and their PL). If the armor is already magical, add its PL to calculate the cost of the spell. You must also know the spells specified for the desired effect(s).',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(202,'Enchant Focus','[Su, AoO]','Arcane - Transmutation\\nDivine - Retribution\\nPsi - Metacreativity',NULL,'7+TPC AP','V (+0), Silent (+2)\\nS (+0), Still (+2)','1 PP per total PL','Tch (+0)','Encounter (D; +0)\\nOngoing (+4; 1 PP/h)\\nPermanent (D; +8; 100 XP cost per PL)','1 focus (+0)','Enchants a focus with an enhancement bonus to attack and damage. Other effects can also be added, specifically those item modifications that have a focus as preferred item type.\\nThe casting costs 1 PP per resulting PL of the focus (see the item modification list for possible effects and their PL). If the focus is already magical, add its PL to calculate the cost of the spell. You must also know the spells specified for the desired effect(s).',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(203,'Enchant Shield','[Su, AoO]','Arcane - Abjuration and Transmutation\\nDivine - Protection\\nPsi - Metacreativity',NULL,'7+TPC AP','V (+0), Silent (+2)\\nS (+0), Still (+2)','1 PP per total PL','Tch (+0)','Encounter (D; +0)\\nOngoing (+4; 1 PP/h)\\nPermanent (D; +8; 100 XP cost per PL)','1 shield (+0)','Enchants a shield with an enhancement bonus to parry. Other effects can also be added, specifically those item modifications that have shield as preferred item type.\\nThe casting costs 1 PP per resulting PL of the shield (see the item modification list for possible effects and their PL). If the shield is already magical, add its PL to calculate the cost of the spell. You must also know the spells specified for the desired effect(s).',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(204,'Enchant Weapon','[Su, AoO]','Arcane - Transmutation\\nDivine - Retribution\\nDivine - Animals (only for natural weapons)\\nPsi - Metacreativity (only for non-natural weapons)\\nPsi - Psychometabolism (only for natural weapons)\\nArcane Archery (only for bows and arrows)',NULL,'7+TPC AP','V (+0), Silent (+2)\\nS (+0), Still (+2)','1 PP per total PL','Tch (+0)','Encounter (D; +0)\\nOngoing (+4; 1 PP/h)\\nPermanent (D; +8; 100 XP cost per PL)','1 weapon or 50 projectiles (+0)','Enchants a weapon with an enhancement bonus to attack and damage. Natural attacks can also be enchanted, but note that each attack form counts as one weapon (in other words, one casting will not enhance all of a creature\'s natural attacks). Projectiles receive only a damage bonus (not an attack bonus). Other effects can also be added, specifically those item modifications that have weapon as preferred item type.\\nThe casting costs 1 PP per resulting PL of the weapon (see the item modification list for possible effects and their PL). If the weapon is already magical, add its PL to calculate the cost of the spell. You must also know the spells specified for the desired effect(s).',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(205,'Contingency','[Su, AoO]','Arcane - Abjuration and Ouranomancy\\nDivine - Protection\\nPsi - Metacreativity and Psychometabolism',NULL,'10 min (+0)\\n1 min (+4)\\n1 r (+8)','V (+0), Silent (+2)\\nS (+0), Still (+2)\\nF (small statuette worth 100 sp per PL of triggered spell)','7 PP','Personal (+0)','Ongoing (+0; 1 PP/h)\\nPermanent (D; +8)','You and one spell (+0)','This spell sets up a trigger condition that activates a second spell. The second spell must be cast by you directly after the Contingency spell, it must have only you as target, and it must not have a higher PP cost than half the Contingency\'s PL.\\nThe second spell will not activate nor start counting its duration until the triggering condition has been met. The spell will take effect after the triggering condition has been resolved, and it cannot be used to interrupt an ongoing action.\\nThe trigger can be based on any condition affecting your person, including bloodied, unconscious, exhausted, et. al., but it cannot trigger on exact levels of HP, SP, or PP. It can also be based on anything perceived by your senses (or recognized by your Knowledge and Linguistics skills), but it will be fooled by anything that successfully fools your senses.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(206,'Trigger','[Su, AoO]','Arcane - Abjuration and Divination\\nDivine - Insight and Protection\\nPsi - Clairsentience and Metacreativity','Special','10 min (+0)\\n1 min (+4)\\n1 r (+8)','V (+0), Silent (+2)\\nS (+0), Still (+2)\\nM (powdered gems worth 100 sp per PL of triggered spell)','3 PP for touch trigger\\n+2 PP for +15 Spot\\n+2 PP for +15 Listen\\n+4 PP for +20 Spot\\n+4 PP for +20 Listen\\n+6 PP for +25 Spot\\n+6 PP for +25 Listen','Tch (+0)','Ongoing (+0; 1 PP/h)\\nPermanent (D; +8)','1 location or object plus one spell (+0)','This spell creates a magical touch sensor at a location or on an object, and then sets up a second spell to be activated by the sensor. The second spell must be cast by you directly after the Trigger spell, it must be centered on the target, it must target an area or the triggering creature(s) or objects present during the casting, and it must not have a higher PP cost than half the Trigger\'s PL.\\nThe second spell will not activate nor start counting its duration until the triggering condition has been met. The spell will take effect after the triggering condition has been resolved, and it cannot be used to interrupt an ongoing action. If the triggered spell involves an attack roll, replace it with d20! + (PL of the Trigger).\\nThe Trigger is invisible, but it can be detected and disabled as a magical trap of the appropriate PL.\\nThe trigger can be based on anything perceived by the sensor (recognition of creatures, words, etc. are limited by the caster\'s Knowledge and Linguistics skills), but it can potentially be fooled by invisibility and illusions.\\nSpot: The sensor has normal vision and can make reactive Spot checks.\\nListen: The sensor has normal hearing and can make reactive Listen checks.','Spot options: The sensor has normal vision and can make reactive Spot checks.\\nListen options: The sensor has normal hearing and can make reactive Listen checks.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(207,'Force Armor','[Su, MR, AoO, Force]','Arcane - Abjuration and Kinetomancy\\nPsi - Metacreativity and Psychokinesis',NULL,'7+TPC AP','V (+0), Silent (+2)\\nS (+0), Still (+2)','1 PP for +2 bonus\\n+3 PP per extra +1 (up to +10 total)','Tch (+0)\\nClose (+3; LoS)','Ongoing (+0; 1 PP/h)\\nPermanent (D; +8; 100 XP cost per PL)','1 creature (+0)\\n2 creatures (+2)\\n3-4 creatures (+4)\\n5-8 creatures (+6)\\n9-16 creatures (+8)\\nL creatures count as 2, H as 4, G as 8, and C as 16','This spell envelops the target\'s body in a force field that provides an armor bonus to DR (without hindering movement at all).',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(208,'Analyze Creature','[Su, AoO]','Arcane - Divination\\nDivine - Insight\\nPsi - Clairsentience','Spellcasting check vs. 10 + target CL','7+TPC AP','V (+0), Silent (+2)\\nS (+0), Still (+2)','3 PP','Tch (+0)\\nClose (+3; LoS)\\nMedium (+6; LoS)','Instantaneous (+0)','1 creature (+0)','You try to identify the target creature and discover its strengths and weaknesses.',NULL,'S - You identify the creature\'s race, templates, class, and approximate CL.\\nES - You also discover the target\'s resistances, immunities, vulnerabilities, and special abilities.\\nCS - You discover all base characteristics of the target\'s race and templates.\\nF - You identify the target\'s race but nothing else.',NULL,NULL,NULL);
